{"tid":1063182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吐露港公路兩車相撞 傷者送院不治","createTime":"2019-03-15T14:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T18:16:21.000Z","uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6103168c8e0df148f0dfb3dd1e8c198005881906","tid":1063182,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T14:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190315/large/1552658485_b406.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190315%2Flarge%2F1552658485_b406.jpg&h=d7080723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吐露港公路發生奪命車禍，晚上9時許，據報兩部車沿上址往九龍方向行駛，途至馬窩對開時相撞。現場消息稱，有兩人受傷，其中一名傷者意外後倒卧馬路上。救援人員趕往現場，將重創傷者送院搶救，惜證實不治。<br />\n受事件影響，吐露港公路往九龍方向近馬窩的部份行車線封閉，駕駛人士只可使用餘下行車線行車。運輸署呼籲駕駛人士考慮改用其他道路，現時上址交通繁忙。"},{"pid":"059d9f3ba33448c8d3212b039becb9a14c0ffa47","tid":1063182,"uid":117200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T14:58:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">網民留言:神迴避</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190315/59374180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190315%2F59374180&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=84fbf134\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190315%2F59374180&h=2874bd92\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190315/59374180</a>"},{"pid":"865da8cd2220b3f494677763347ca6f8e28c5f98","tid":1063182,"uid":138499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:00:56.000Z","msg":"嘩屌  又撞到飛埋出嚟"},{"pid":"5a8e13278c2bc213252e9cfc50bf32ba2cb0a3aa","tid":1063182,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:07:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">網民爆料:司機沒死,是後來落車再被其他車輛撞倒</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190315/photo/bkn-20190315215536238-0315_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190315230031\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190315%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190315215536238-0315_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190315230031&h=a1de3ac9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c79cd4fd09046a7bf3c5bad7114b139b69ddffc","tid":1063182,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:07:22.000Z","msg":"好似前幾日先死左個agt<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe34669d395a51bd3c6de5d367a8935678d1cca","tid":1063182,"uid":162511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:11:53.000Z","msg":"吐露港猛鬼公路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd35d125d7a85527bca39787436a1384bfcf7e0","tid":1063182,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:13:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">吐露港公路兩貨Van撞1死1傷</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大埔吐露港公路發生嚴重交通意外，今晚(15日)9時許，兩輛輕型貨車依次沿吐露港公路往九龍方向行駛，當駛至馬窩對開時，白色輕型貨車突然失控，撞向右邊石壆後橫亘路中，另一輛GoGoVan懷疑收掣不及從後猛撞，1人倒臥地上嚴重受傷，送院後不治，另1人報稱腰痛，由救護車送往那打素醫院治理。"},{"pid":"8c5d5148c686157078b6f88273b95f8c44809f7a","tid":1063182,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bd35d125d7a85527bca39787436a1384bfcf7e0","tid":1063182,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:13:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">吐露港公路兩貨Van撞1死1傷</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大埔吐露港公路發生嚴重交通意外，今晚(15日)9時許，兩輛輕型貨車依次沿吐露港公路往九龍方向行駛，當駛至馬窩對開時，白色輕型貨車突然失控，撞向右邊石壆後橫亘路中，另一輛GoGoVan懷疑收掣不及從後猛撞，1人倒臥地上嚴重受傷，送院後不治，另1人報稱腰痛，由救護車送往那打素醫院治理。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190315/photo/bkn-20190315215536238-0315_00822_001_08b.jpg?20190315231123\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190315%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190315215536238-0315_00822_001_08b.jpg%3F20190315231123&h=e4500fdf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1138e3b14039806144ed3cfa70970706c56f0a6","tid":1063182,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/54361749_2325188610844846_8772090464330317824_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=d1b620f800d30783f24b85897029badf&amp;oe=5D08E1BF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F54361749_2325188610844846_8772090464330317824_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3Dd1b620f800d30783f24b85897029badf%26oe%3D5D08E1BF&h=7ad81f7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f33924e40e0eb361663f199ff27f29fd0a8042cb","tid":1063182,"uid":69976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1138e3b14039806144ed3cfa70970706c56f0a6","tid":1063182,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/54361749_2325188610844846_8772090464330317824_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=d1b620f800d30783f24b85897029badf&amp;oe=5D08E1BF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F54361749_2325188610844846_8772090464330317824_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3Dd1b620f800d30783f24b85897029badf%26oe%3D5D08E1BF&h=7ad81f7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:22:44.000Z","msg":"後車司機仆街了"},{"pid":"bf4d9b60f020f9c155d07db21a9ad5dfca73396b","tid":1063182,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" 